, Atari 5200, Atari 8-bit family, Commodore 64, ColecoVision, VIC-20, and IBM PC. The PC version was developed by Sierra On-Line and is incompatible with everything except an original IBM PC/XT with a CGA video card.\n\nIn the Atari-ported versions the hero is named Sir Dudley, and the girl, married to Sir Dudley, is Lady Penelope.","total_rating":67.95884364487071,"total_rating_count":10,"url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/jungle-hunt","videos":[{"id":83190,"video_id":"_Ey3dzEjlec"}],"websites":[{"id":358410,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/Jungle%20Hunt","type":{"id":6,"type":"Twitch"}},{"id":524023,"url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jungle_Hunt","type":{"id":3,"type":"Wikipedia"}},{"id":524022,"url":"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCkyPfa0irbEJX14em0Sir6Q","type":{"id":9,"type":"YouTube"}}]}